# Block all heavy dependencies across the entire monorepo

**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/**pycache**/

# Block local build caches

**/.expo/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/android/
\*\*/ios/

# Block large local databases

**/\*.db
**/\*.sqlite3

# Block Git history (EAS doesn't need your commit history to build)

.git/
